title: Certificates
agents: linux
catalog: app/postfix
license: GPL
distribution: arsoft
description:
 Checks certificates used by the postfix server for expiring certificates.

 Returns {WARN} if the certificate will expire within the next 60 days.

 Returns {CRIT} if the certificate will expire within the next 30 days or
 already is expired.

item:
 Name of the certificate.

inventory:
 Creates one Check for every certificate in the agent's output.
